{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/41622", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/41622/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/41622/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/41622/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/41622", "id": 225239298, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUyMjUyMzkyOTg=", "number": 41622, "title": "MutexGuard<Cell<i32>> must not be Sync", "user": {"login": "RalfJung", "id": 330628, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzMDYyOA==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/330628?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung", "html_url": "https://github.com/RalfJung", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 267612997, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyNjc2MTI5OTc=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/I-unsound", "name": "I-unsound", "color": "e11d21", "default": false, "description": "Issue: A soundness hole (worst kind of bug), see: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Soundness"}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2017-04-29T07:11:01Z", "updated_at": "2017-05-03T03:24:43Z", "closed_at": "2017-05-03T03:24:43Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Right now, `MutexGuard<Cell<i32>>` satisfies the `Sync` bound. That is rather bad, because it lets me write a program that has a data race:\r\n```rust\r\nuse std::sync::Mutex;\r\nuse std::cell::Cell;\r\n\r\nextern crate rayon;\r\n\r\nfn main()\r\n{\r\n    let m = Mutex::new(Cell::new(0));\r\n    let g = m.lock().unwrap();\r\n    {\r\n        rayon::join(\r\n            || { g.set(g.get() + 1); println!(\"Thread 1: {:?}\", g.get()) },\r\n            || { g.set(g.get() + 1); println!(\"Thread 2: {:?}\", g.get()) });\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\nThe `get` and `set` calls in the two threads are unsynchronized (as usual for a `Cell`), and they are racing. This is a soundness bug.\r\n\r\nThe cause for this is that `MutexGuard<T>` implements `Sync` whenever `T` implements `Send`, which is plain wrong. The fix is to let `MutexGuard<T>` implement `Sync` whenever `T` implements `Sync`. I will submit a PR soon.", "closed_by": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors", "html_url": "https://github.com/bors", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/41622/reactions", "total_count": 23, "+1": 23, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/41622/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}